data.description: Welcome to this hidden gem that holds promise for both savvy investors and enthusiastic first-time homebuyers with a passion for minor renovation.  Structurally sound, this property requires only cosmetic upgrades for a modern touch.  A unique opportunity to create a dream home tailored to your personal style and preference.  The generous floor plan provides ample space.  Retains charming architectural details for added character.  Spacious yard and enclosed patio area, providing additional opportunities for outdoor living and entertainment. With a little landscaping, this space can be transformed into a charming oasis. Don't miss out on the chance to turn this home into your own shining masterpiece. **THIS HOME DOES NOT MEET FHA OR VA PROPERTY STANDARDS.  CONVENTIONAL, CASH, OR FHA 203K OFFERS ARE ACCEPTABLE.
